### 9.3 多语言验签代码（完整保留）

#### Java

```Java

public static boolean validateSign(String data, String sign, String publicKey) {
    try {
        Signature signature = Signature.getInstance("SHA256WithRSA");
        PublicKey pubKey = getPublicKeyFromX509("RSA", publicKey);
        signature.initVerify(pubKey);
        signature.update(data.getBytes());
        return signature.verify(Base64.decode(sign));
    } catch (Exception e) {
        e.printStackTrace();
        return false;
    }
}
```

#### Python

```Python

from Crypto.PublicKey import RSA
from Crypto.Signature import PKCS1_v1_5
from Crypto.Hash import SHA256
import base64

h = SHA256.new(body.encode())
pubKey = RSA.importKey(PUBLIC_KEY)
verifier = PKCS1_v1_5.new(pubKey)
verifier.verify(h, base64.b64decode(sign))
```

#### PHP

```PHP

$data = file_get_contents("php://input");
$sign = getallheaders()['Authorization'];
$pubKey = "公钥";
$result = openssl_verify(
    $data,
    base64_decode($sign),
    $pubKey,
    OPENSSL_ALGO_SHA256
) === 1;
```

### 9.4 回调响应规则

- 验签通过 → **返回字符串 success**

- 否则收钱吧会重试：1s→5s→30s→600s

